TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT id_pecul , period_datos , id_colect , id_control , id_busqueda , TO_CHAR(resul_control) , TO_CHAR(is_real_forzado) , case when resul_control='ok' then 1 when resul_control='ko' then 2 else 3 end as id_estado , mensaje FROM ( SELECT id_pecul , period_datos , id_colect , id_control , id_busqueda , is_real_forzado , mensaje ,resul_control ,RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY id_pecul, period_datos, id_colect, id_control, id_busqueda ORDER BY IS_REAL_FORZADO DESC) AS RANKING FROM ( select a.id_pecul , a.period_datos , a.id_colect , a.id_control , a.id_busqueda , a.resul_control as resul_control , 'Real' as is_real_forzado , a.mensaje from t_gld_hch_res_control a inner join t_gld_rel_colect_control b on a.id_colect=b.id_colect and a.id_control=b.id_control union select a.id_pecul , a.period_datos , a.id_colect , b.id_control , a.id_busqueda ,'warning' as resul_control ,'Forzado' as is_real_forzado , a.mensaje from t_gld_hch_res_control a left join t_gld_rel_colect_control b on a.id_colect=b.id_colect and a.id_control<>b.id_control ) ) WHERE RANKING=1 and period_datos = $$ParamPeriodoDatos

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(RESUL_CONTROL='warning' and IS_REAL_FORZADO='Forzado','No tenemos informacion del control',MENSAJE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: OBSERVACIONES
